{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/administrator/v1/deployment/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Portal Docs"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9dd6537c-ba07-5eac-ad65-03624e8492c3","html":"<h1>Deployments</h1>\n<p>There are two ways that Kudoo supports you releasing new versions of your app. Automated and manual.</p>\n<h2>Automated deployments</h2>\n<p>To get started using automated deployments there is some setup you’ll need to perform.</p>\n<p>We use <a href=\"https://drone.io/\">Drone</a> for our Automated deployments. </p>\n<p>Once you signed up for Kudoo cloud through the <a href=\"https://portal.kudoo.io\">Portal</a> all you need to do to activate your Drone account is to visit <a href=\"https://drone.kudoo.io\">https://drone.kudoo.io</a> and then authorise the application.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Authorise Drone\"\n        title=\"Authorise Drone\"\n        src=\"/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/fcda8/drone-authorisation.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/12f09/drone-authorisation.png 148w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/e4a3f/drone-authorisation.png 295w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/fcda8/drone-authorisation.png 590w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/efc66/drone-authorisation.png 885w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/c83ae/drone-authorisation.png 1180w,\n/static/720462b55e1b7e6fe35945909da33ade/29114/drone-authorisation.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\nYou will now have access to Drone.</p>\n<p>You can now open the <code class=\"language-text\">web-app</code> repository\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/f43e4/drone-repo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.05357142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Web app repository\"\n        title=\"Web app repository\"\n        src=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/fcda8/drone-repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/12f09/drone-repo.png 148w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/e4a3f/drone-repo.png 295w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/fcda8/drone-repo.png 590w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/efc66/drone-repo.png 885w,\n/static/ec5555b59543c16a9c400f2cb12df1e2/f43e4/drone-repo.png 1120w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Under the source directory there will be a file called <code class=\"language-text\">.drone.yml</code>. </p>\n<h3>Configuring your Pipelines</h3>\n<p>In order for your deployments to work you’ll need to enter the <code class=\"language-text\">secrets</code> of your application.</p>\n<p>NODE<em>ENV=development\nGRAPHQL</em>API<em>URL=<a href=\"http://localhost:4000/api/\">http://localhost:4000/api/</a>\nSKELM</em>BASE_URL=<a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a></p>\n<h2>Manual deployments</h2>\n<p>To do this you’ll need to clone you app your app locally.</p>\n<p>You’ll need to make sure you have <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\">Node installed</a></p>\n<p>Then make sure you are using the correct version. As of this writing, the latest LTS version of Node is version 12. </p>\n<p><strong>Please note</strong> Kudoo will always use the currently active LTS node release.</p>\n<p>Now make sure you have <a href=\"https://github.com/firebase/firebase-tools\">Firebase Tools</a> installed by running:\n<code class=\"language-text\">npm install -g firebase-tools</code></p>\n<p>You can now run\n<code class=\"language-text\">firebase deploy</code>\nto deploy your app.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":""}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"c52c60cc-90e3-5384-a26d-6ccbb8e4b552","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/datamodel/"}}},{"node":{"id":"19def933-56ac-5852-a59b-5cd7e9bb37bc","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/overview/"}}},{"node":{"id":"39bb2a5c-0235-5a63-a56b-05ee21fde39e","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/menu-screens/"}}},{"node":{"id":"a72831f1-dc5f-5b3d-9b53-1a1289227d93","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/documents/"}}},{"node":{"id":"9fe9fe24-ba90-5a03-aa64-c1b0953f258d","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/pubsub/"}}},{"node":{"id":"9098952d-032a-524c-bc81-c1e4af1aa6e5","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/screens/"}}},{"node":{"id":"81f160fe-d0d8-5125-89e1-7ed7cd6ecba5","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/administrator/v1/billing/"}}},{"node":{"id":"3cb09b97-3448-5719-be2e-75f4783ec0cf","frontmatter":{"title":""},"fields":{"slug":"/developer/v1/widgets/"}}},{"node":{"id":"b21a2bc6-871f-5b02-819f-31